Add title and Slicers 11

1.  Insert a Text box and Rename it to Mentally Ill Killed by Police (Segoe Bold 18 font). Turn on the border in the format and set background color to white and transparency to 63%.

2. From the visuals pane, Add three slicers Titled Year Month and Quarter. Turn on the borders and set background color to blue with 82% transparency. Turn on the slicer header and under it set font color to white and background color to black and font size 12.

3. Make the slicer a drop down and format it as shown below.

4. Click on the colaberry logo and select bring to front and super impose it on your title text box as shown in end pic
